/Users/seanross/kingdom_of_god/home-base/current_hunts/big-thinkers/research-systems/codex-philosopher-atlas/missions/beyond-de-giorgi/planning-runs/run-010/attacks/chain-02.md:18:- The kill condition is undercalibrated. The branch should die not only when the observable is undefined without smooth-flow debt, but also when the only honest definition already requires a proxy class whose bridge burden is essentially a regularity theorem in disguise.
